Steps to intgrate Disqus into your Hugo website  Sign up: First of all you have to sign up for Disqus.  Create an account on Disqus.  
 Install Disqus: You are offered two choices after the registration process. Select &lsquo;I want to install Disqus on my site&rsquo;. Choose &lsquo;Install Disqus&rsquo;  
 Fill in the form: Disqus needs some information for adding a forum to your website.
